=== TEST 1: hello, ngx_php7
This is just a simple demonstration of the
echo directive provided by ngx_php7.
--- config
location = /t {
    content_by_php '
        echo "hello ngx_php7!\n";
    ';
}
--- request
GET /t
--- response_body
hello ngx_php7!



